values:
Ok So since I have nothing better to do with my life, I will tell you how my summer has been. It's been amazing so far. The only thing I wish to change would be seeing more of my friends. But I've been hanging out with Johnners a lot and that's pretty cool, no really cool ;) I just got back from Las Vegas and it was HOT. Almost 116 everyday. I saw John Monday night for the first time in 10 1/2 days, and he suprised me with flowers. Gosh I love him =) Yesterday we had dance; part if the "two day" and we had a lot of fun. Today I cleaned the basement for my madre and layed outside man is it hot! I really wish I had a car so I could drive ANYWHERE I wanted to, oh well in 4 months!!! Yea. So yea well more later but for now see ya'll


<3 Em
xoxoxo
